<div class="socs-feature">
<h3><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e9da8db6c05d">UPDATE as of 4/17/2020</a></h3>
<p>     As per Governor Greg Abbott's executive order (4/17/2020) all public schools will remain closed for face-to-face instruction for the remainder of the 2019/2020 school year.   

   Please use the following link  (click read more)  for more important information:    https://3.files.edl.io/9166/ 20/04/17/233629-cdd71243-4454- 48e0-a033-1d21d61b73e9.jpg    
  

   
</p>
<p class="socs-feature-read-more"><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e9da8db6c05d" aria-label="Read more about UPDATE as of 4/17/2020">read more</a></p>
</div>
<div class="socs-feature">
<h3><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e83a06c831d7">UPDATE as of 3/31/20</a></h3>
<p>  Vysehrad ISD will follow the extended social distancing guidelines set by President Trump and the Executive Order by Texas Governor Greg Abbott and will remain closed through April 30, 2020.  
</p>
<p class="socs-feature-read-more"><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e83a06c831d7" aria-label="Read more about UPDATE as of 3/31/20">read more</a></p>
</div>
<div class="socs-feature">
<h3><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e821297654d4">UPDATE as of 3/30/2020</a></h3>
<p>   Packet drop off for last week's packets and pick up for the new packets is Thursday, April 2.    

    THERE HAS BEEN A CHANGE IN DROP OFF/ PICK UP TIMES    

    All Grade   levels should drop off old and pick up new packets from 5:00 - 6:00 pm.    

   Please enter through the far driveway and exit through the driveway near the front of the school. Please continue to check our website for updates. Thank you for your support and stay well!   

   REMINDER: If you did not turn in your child's Vysehrad Library book last week, please turn it in this Thursday.  Thank you!   
</p>
<p class="socs-feature-read-more"><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e821297654d4" aria-label="Read more about UPDATE as of 3/30/2020">read more</a></p>
</div>
<div class="socs-feature">
<h3><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e78df3ba4ccd">UPDATE as of 3-23-2020 Pick-up for Instructional Materials</a></h3>
<p> Vysehrad ISD Staff will be preparing instructional materials for students starting March 23. Instructional material (online and/or via pickup) will be available starting  Thursday, March 26.  

  Vysehrad ISD will have packet/ informational pickup for Pre-K thru 4th grades on Thursday from 5:00-5:45 pm and for 5th - 8th grades from 5:45 - 6:30 pm.  Please enter through the 3rd driveway as we do for afternoon pickup. We will deliver the materials to your vehicle. Please remain in your vehicle. Parents should return completed packets on Thursday, April 2, at the previously mentioned times. We also ask that all library books that are . . . </p>
<p class="socs-feature-read-more"><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/5e78df3ba4ccd" aria-label="Read more about UPDATE as of 3-23-2020 Pick-up for Instructional Materials">read more</a></p>
</div>
<div class="socs-feature">
