<p>       Vysehrad Independent School District Pre-Kindergarten and Kindergarten Visitation/Registration for the 2020-2021 school year will be held on Tuesday, April 14, 2020 from 5:00-6:00 pm in conjunction with an ice-cream social. (This will be before the 6pm PTO Meeting. )  After this date, you may call or visit during regular school hours.   

      

